The package boost-ublas is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS numeric_ublas)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_ublas)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_ublas REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_ublas)
